      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented version control, unit testing, and regression test suite covering blood pump flow regimes.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R1 used under institutional software quality plan. Version-controlled input decks stored in Git repository with SHA-verified checksums. Regression suite of 14 canonical flow cases executed at each solver update; all pass within 0.5% tolerance."
    },
    {
