      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate second-order spatial accuracy on manufactured solution benchmark for incompressible rotating-frame flow.",
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions applied to rotating-frame incompressible Navier-Stokes equations. Observed convergence order of 1.97 on velocity components and 1.94 on pressure, confirming nominally second-order accuracy. Results consistent with published ANSYS verification documentation."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/factor/discretization-error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
