      "rationale": "Richardson extrapolation-based GCI computed across three mesh levels. GCI for wall shear stress (primary hemolysis driver) was 1.8% at medium mesh; GCI for velocity magnitude at impeller exit was 2.1%. Both exceed the acceptance threshold, justifying use of the 4.8M cell medium mesh for all production simulations."
    },
