      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental data obtained at matched operating points: flow rates 2.5–6.0 L/min, rotational speeds 2500–3500 RPM, blood analog viscosity 3.5 cP. Boundary condition uncertainty propagation documented; maximum mismatch in inlet velocity profile 4.2%, within acceptable range for MRL 2."
    },
