      "rationale": "NIH and RH are established regulatory quantities for blood pump hemolysis assessment per FDA guidance. Wall shear stress distribution directly drives the power-law hemolysis model. All QoIs traceable to clinical hemolysis endpoints and the RH < 1 regulatory acceptance criterion for Class II CPB devices."
